SPORT: The League Cup Final Highlights
On: BBC 1 HD

Manish Bhasin introduces action from the 2014 League Cup final at Wembley Stadium between Manchester City and Sunderland, as City manager Manuel Pellegrini goes in search of what could potentially be the first of three domestic trophies this year.
